2. WorldQuant "101 Formulaic Alphas"
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The alpha formulas transcribed in `alphagauntlet/wq101/` (the alpha005,
alpha020, alpha024, alpha077, ... families) are implementations of formulas
published in:

    Zura Kakushadze, "101 Formulaic Alphas",
    Wilmott Magazine, 2016 (84), pp. 72-81.
    arXiv:1601.00991

These are re-implementations of publicly published formulas for research and
evaluation purposes. Please cite the original paper if you use them in academic
or published work.

